### ===== PRODUCTS =====

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID

### Create new product
POST http://localhost:3000/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gaming Laptop",
    "description": "High-performance laptop with RTX 4090 graphics",
    "price": 1299.99,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "inStock": true,
    "quantity": 25,
    "brand": "Dell"
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gaming Laptop Pro",
    "description": "Ultra high-performance laptop with RTX 4090 Ti",
    "price": 1499.99,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "inStock": true,
    "quantity": 15,
    "brand": "Dell"
}

### Delete product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID HTTP/1.1

